OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"You've failed hundreds of islanders,
OL,8,Fand that is unforgivable" - that is
OL,9,Fone Jersey patient's view after she
OL,10,Freceived a letter confirming she had
OL,11,Fosteoporosis, despite medical
OL,12,Fprofessionals assuring her she did not
OL,13,Feight years ago.
OL,15,FMarina Mauger is among the more than
OL,16,F250 patients for whom a review
OL,17,Fidentified potential concerns with
OL,18,Ftheir diagnoses and treatments after
OL,19,Fbone density scans conducted between
OL,20,FJanuary 2017 and January 2022.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,FThe letter also revealed that Marina
OL,8,Fis among the 20 people who may have
OL,9,Fbeen 'moderately harmed' by advice and
OL,10,Fcare given to her at the time.
OL,12,F"I was horrified," she told ITV News.
OL,13,F"When you open a letter, and it
OL,14,Fsuddenly says, 'We know you had a
OL,15,Fbonescan in 2018, and you were told it
OL,16,Fwas all good. Well, with no treatment,
OL,17,Fwe have suddenly reviewed your scans,
OL,18,Fand you have had osteoporosis for
OL,19,Feight years.'
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"What difference will it make to my
OL,8,Fhealth to have not started the
OL,9,Fmedication and to start it now, eight
OL,10,Fyears later.
OL,12,F"I think that's a question everyone
OL,13,Fshould be asking."
OL,15,FPotential issues were highlighted
OL,16,Fduring the review of the island's
OL,17,Frheumatology service.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,FSpecialist independent consultants,
OL,8,Fhired by Health and Care Jersey (HCJ),
OL,9,Fhave now reviewed all 1,000 scans in
OL,10,Fthis period.
OL,12,FOf those, the consultants advised more
OL,13,Fthan 250 patients should undertake a
OL,14,Fre-scan to "monitor any changes to
OL,15,Fbone density".
OL,17,FA further 20 patients received a 'duty
OL,18,Fof candour' letter, saying that the
OL,19,Ftreatment and care those patients had
OL,20,Ffollowing their scan "fell below the
OL,21,Flevel that would have been expected".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,FMarina was diagnosed with breast
OL,8,Fcancer in 2018 and was referred for a
OL,9,Fscan because her cancer treatment
OL,10,Fcould have weakened her bones.
OL,12,FShe was assured at the time that her
OL,13,Fbones were not thinning, but the
OL,14,Fletter she received recently said the
OL,15,Fscan had actually shown she had
OL,16,Fosteoporosis - a condition that
OL,17,Fweakens bones, making them fragile.
OL,19,FIn 2023, Marina fractured her left
OL,20,Fwrist and had also previously
OL,21,Ffractured her ankle.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,FMarina showed ITV News the letter,
OL,8,Fwhich said that if she had been
OL,9,Freceiving the correct treatment and
OL,10,Fmedication, "the risk of sustaining
OL,11,F(the wrist) fracture would have been
OL,12,Freduced".
OL,14,FShe says she received the "terrifying
OL,15,Fletter" with no warning, phone call or
OL,16,Fcontact.
OL,18,F"I did say to the consultant, 'Do you
OL,19,Fnot think that you might have been
OL,20,Fbetter to ring people and say this has
OL,21,Fcome to light?'
OL,26,@sD@ApmsD@Kpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"But he said there were so many of us,
OL,8,Fthey thought it would be best to send
OL,9,Fa letter.
OL,11,F"I was one of the first 20, but there
OL,12,Fare actually 270 people they found
OL,13,Fwith dodgy results. How does that
OL,14,Fhappen? Who is checking who?"
OL,16,F"The consultant also told me that
OL,17,Fbecause I was borderline (in 2018), I
OL,18,Fshould have had bone scans every two
OL,19,Fyears, but I had nothing for eight
OL,20,Fyears."
OL,26,@yD@ZpmyD@bpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,FMarina says that the experience has
OL,8,Fleft her mistrusting the health
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,F"Eight years of no treatment, and
OL,12,Fduring those eight years, I have had
OL,13,Fto have multiple follow-up surgeries
OL,14,Ffor the cancer; anything could have
OL,15,Fhappened to me.
OL,17,F"I am having spinal surgery, and I am
OL,18,Fgoing to Taunton to have it, so that
OL,19,Fsays all you need to know about my
OL,20,Ftrust in Jersey's health service.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"The fact that they have no records of
OL,8,Fthe cancer drug I was on for three
OL,9,Fyears, no record of the letter which
OL,10,Fwas sent to my oncologist, which said
OL,11,Fmy bone density was good, what does
OL,12,Fthat tell you?
OL,14,F"I have very, very little confidence
OL,15,Fin any of them, really."
OL,17,FIn a statement, Simon West, Medical
OL,18,FDirector for Health and Care Jersey,
OL,19,Fsays: "I'm sorry to hear that a
OL,20,Fpatient was upset to receive the news
OL,21,Fvia letter. That was not our intention.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"Our aim was to set out the facts
OL,8,Fclearly and easily to try to alleviate
OL,9,Fany concerns patients may have.
OL,11,F"We also included a telephone number
OL,12,Fto our PALS service for people to ring
OL,13,Fand to ask any questions that they may
OL,14,Fhave. Affected patients have also been
OL,15,Fable to discuss the specifics of their
OL,16,Fcase with one of the specialist
OL,17,Findependent consultants who undertook
OL,18,Fthe review.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"We will shortly begin inviting
OL,8,Faffected patients for a rescan and
OL,9,Fhave set ourselves the target of
OL,10,Fcompleting all rescans by the end of
OL,11,FMay.
OL,13,F"Reviews are common practice across
OL,14,Fall health organisations to assess
OL,15,Fwhether services are fit for purpose,
OL,16,Fand islanders can be reassured that
OL,17,Fthe care delivered by HCJ is safe and
OL,18,Fof a high standard.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/12
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1776272750
OL,3,C'Unforgivable': Patient given new
OL,4,Cdiagnosis eight years after bone
OL,5,Cdensity scan
OL,7,F"However, my door is always open to
OL,8,Fanyone who has a concern about their
OL,9,Fmedical treatment, as the quality and
OL,10,Fsafety of our services are paramount
OL,11,Fto us."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/12
